# Title: Steganography Unzip Hidden Information From Picture File
# Author: Pawel Mazur
# Date: 2021-09-09
# Level: low
# Description: Detects extracting of zip file from image file
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1027.003
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/auditd/execve/lnx_auditd_unzip_hidden_zip_files_steganography.yml

a0="unzip" type="EXECVE" a1 IN ("*.jpg", "*.png")